    "In the areas of Basic Sciences and Sports, both were answered correctly at higher rates than other topics.",
    "Post hoc analysis found that these used correct answer with no logic (CN) and incorrect answer with inconsistent logic (IIC) at higher frequencies than other pairings.",
    "These results indicate that ChatGPT may be mimicking the cognitive processing of test taking.",
    "In these situations, individuals either answer correctly with a firm resolve, or get stuck on questions and must develop a rationale for an incorrect answer or educated guess.",
    "Further work to improve the knowledge and reasoning level of ChatGPT is needed in order to have it answer accurately at increased rates."
